quran[44]{c,v,t}:
  38,52,"“Ndipo (ku Munda wamtenderewo) adzakhala ndi akazi oyang’ana amuna awo okha basi, ofanana misinkhu"
  38,53,“Izi ndi zomwe mukulonjezedwa pa tsiku la chiweruziro
  38,54,“Ndithu izi ndizopatsa Zathu zosatha
  38,55,"“Awa ndimalipiro (a oopa Allah)! Koma opyola malire (ndi kunyoza aneneri awo), ali ndi mabwelero oipa"
  38,56,“(Omwe ndi) Jahannam adzailowa (ndi kupseleramo). Taonani kuipa kwa malo wokakhazikikamo
  38,57,"“Awa ndimadzi wotentha kwambiri, ndi mafinya (a anthu a ku Moto). Choncho awalaweko"
  38,58,“Ndi zilango zina zambiri zonga zimenezi zamitundumitundu
  38,59,"“(Kudzanenedwa kwa opyola malire, omwe ndiatsogoleri a opembedza mafano): “Gulu ili lalikulu, lilowa nanu ku Moto; (omwe adali okutsatirani. Ndipo atsogoleri adzati): Siolandiridwa (mwamtendere). Ndithu iwo ngolowa ku Moto.”"
  38,60,"“(Otsatira adzanena): “Ndithu tembeleroli likuyenera inu, (limene mukutitembelera ife) chifukwa inu ndiamene mudadzetsa chilangochi potinyenga ife (ndi kutiitanira kunjira yopotoka), taonani kuipa malo okhazikikamo (Jahannam)!”"
  38,61,"“(Otsatira) adzanena: “E Mbuye wathu! Muonjezereni chilango ku Moto pamwamba pa chilango amene watidzetsera chilangochi.”"
  38,62,"“Ndipo (anthu a ku Moto) adzanena: “Kodi nchifukwa ninji sitikuwaona anthu aja omwe timawawerengera kuti ngoipa (pa dziko lapansi)"
  38,63,“Kodi tidawachitira chipongwe (pa dziko lapansi koma taonani sadalowe nafe ku Moto). Kapena kuti maso athu sakuwaona?”
  38,64,"“Ndithu zimenezo, zokangana anthu a ku Moto nzoona"
  38,65,"“Nena (kwa iwo): “Ndithu ine ndine mchenjezi (wochenjeza za chilango cha Allah). Palibe wopembedzedwa mwachoonadi, koma Allah Mmodzi Yekha Wopambana"
  38,66,"“Mbuye wathambo ndi nthaka, ndi zapakati pake; wamphamvu zoposa; Wokhululuka machimo kwambiri (kwa yemwe walapa ndi kumkhulupirira).”"
  38,67,"“Nena (kwa iwo iwe Mtumiki {s.a.w}): “Ichi (chimene ndakuchenjezani nachochi) ndinkhani yaikulu.”"
  38,68,"““Inu, za chimenechi, mukunyozera!”"
  38,69,““Sindimadziwa chilichonse za akuluakulu a pamwamba (angelo) pamene amakangana (za kulengedwa kwa Adam).”
  38,70,"“Palibe china chimene chavumbulutsidwa kwa ine, koma (kuti ndikuuzeni mawu awa oti): “Ine ndine mchenjezi (wanu) woonekera.”"
  38,71,"“(Akumbutse) pamene Mbuye wako adanena kwa angelo: “Ine ndilenga munthu kuchokera ku dothi, (yemwe ndi Adam).”"
  38,72,"““Ndikammaliza ndi kumuuzira mzimu wochokera kwa Ine, igwani pansi momulemekeza.”"
  38,73,“Choncho angelo onse anagwa pansi momulemekeza
  38,74,"“Kupatula Iblis; adadzikweza, ndipo adali mmodzi mwa okana"
  38,75,"“(Allah) adati: “E iwe Iblis! Nchiyani chakuletsa kugwa pansi ndi kuchilemekeza chimene ndachilenga ndi manja Anga (popanda kutuma wina)? Kodi wadzikweza kapena uli mmodzi wa odziika pamwamba?”"
  38,76,"“(Iblis) adanena: “Ine ndine wabwino kuposa iye (Adam); chifukwa ine mudandilenga kuchokera ku Moto, ndipo iye mudamulenga kuchokera kudongo.”"
  38,77,"“(Allah) adanena (kwa Iblis): “Tuluka m’menemo (m’gulu la angelo apamwamba); ndithu iwe ngopirikitsidwa (ku chifundo cha Allah).”"
  38,78,““Ndipo ndithu matembelero Anga akhala pa iwe kufikira tsiku lamalipiro.”
  38,79,"“(Iblis) adati: “E Mbuye wanga! Ndipatseni nthawi kufikira tsiku louka ku imfa.”"
  38,80,"“(Allah) adati: “Ndithu iwe ndiwe mmodzi wa wopatsidwa nthawi.”"
  38,81,““Kufikira tsiku la nthawi yodziwika (imene yaikidwa).”
  38,82,"“(Iblis) adati: “Choncho kupyolera mu ulemelero Wanu ndikulumbira kuti ndiwasokoneza onse.”"
  38,83,““Kupatula akapolo Anu omwe ali osankhidwa (oyeretsedwa) mwa iwo. (Pa iwo ndilibe nyonga zilizonse).”
  38,84,"“(Allah) adati: “Ndikulumbira mwachoonadi ndipo ndikunena choona.”"
  38,85,"““Ndithudi, ndidzazadzitsa Jahannam ndi ochokera ku mtundu wako ndi omwe adzakutsate mwa iwo (ana a Adam) onse.”"
  38,86,"“Nena (iwe Mtumiki{s.a.w}, kwa anthu ako): “Sindikukupemphani malipiro pa zimenezi ndiponso ine simmodzi wa odzikakamiza (pa zinthu zosandiyenera)"
  38,87,“(Qur’an) sichina koma ndichikumbutso ndi chiphunzitso kwa zolengedwa zonse
  38,88,"“Ndipo posachedwa mudziwa, (inu otsutsa, kuona kwa) nkhani zake.”"
  39,1,"“Kuvumbulutsidwa kwa Buku ili kwachokera kwa Allah, Mwini mphamvu zoposa; Mwini nzeru zakuya"
  39,2,“Ndithu Ife takuvumbulutsira iwe buku ili mwamtheradi; choncho mpembedze Allah momyeretsera mapemphero Iye yekha
  39,3,"“Dziwani kuti Allah Ngolandira mapemphero oyera, (opanda kuphatikizidwa ndi zina). Koma amene adzipangira athandizi kusiya Allah, (akumanena kuti): “Ife sitikuwapembedza awa, koma tikutero ndi cholinga choti atifikitse pafupi ndi Allah.” Ndithu Allah, adzaweruza pakati pawo (pakati pa okhulupirira Allah, ndi okana) pa zimene akusiyana. Ndithu Allah saongola amene ali wabodza; wokanira zedi (Allah)"
  39,4,"“Allah akadafuna kupeza mwana, akadasankha yemwe akum’funa mzomwe adalenga. Wapatukana ndi zimenezo! Iye ndi Allah Mmodzi; Wogonjetsa; (Wochita zimene wafuna)"
  39,5,“Adalenga thambo ndi nthaka mwamtheradi. Amakulunga usiku mu usana; ndipo amakulunga usana mu usiku. Ndipo dzuwa ndi mwezi wazichita kuti zitumikire monga momwe afunira. Zonsezi zikuyenda kufikira pa nthawi yake imene yaikidwa. Dziwani kuti Iye (Allah) Ngwamphamvu zoposa; Ngokhululuka kwambiri
  39,6,"“Adakulengani kuchokera mu mzimu umodzi (womwe ndi Adam; tate wa anthu). Ndipo kenako adalenga kuchokera mu mzimu umenewo mnzake, (mkazi wake, Hawa); ndipo adakutsitsirani mitundu isanu ndi itatu ya nyama ziwiriziwiri (zomwe ndi: Ngamira yaimuna ndi yaikazi, ng’ombe yaimuna ndi yaikazi, mbuzi yaimuna ndi yaikazi ndi nkhosa yaimuna ndi yaikazi. Zonse pamodzi, zisanu ndi zitatu, zomwe mumathandizidwa nazo kwambiri). Amakuumbani m’mimba mwa mayi anu mkaumbidwe kosiyanasiyana, mu mdima utatu; (mu mdima wa mimba, chiberekero ndi mdima wa nembanemba). Ameneyo (adakuchitirani zonsezi), ndi Allah, Mleri wanu; ufumu ngwa Iye. Palibe wopembedzedwa mwa choona, koma Iye. Kodi nanga mukutembunuzidwa bwanji (kusiya Allah)"
  39,7,"“Ngati mukana ndithu Allah Ngodzikwaniritsa sasaukira kwa inu (chikhulupiliro chanu ndi kuthokoza kwanu); koma sakonda kukanira kwa anthu Ake. Ngati mumthokoza (pa mtendere Wake umene uli pa inu) akuyanja kuthokoza kwanuko. Ndipo mzimu wochimwa sungasenze machimo a mzimu wina. Kenako kobwerera kwanu nkwa Mbuye wanu, ndipo adzakuuzani zimene mudali kuchita. Ndithu Iye Ngodziwa (zinsinsi) za m’mitima"